"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"5 habits that the boss must cultivate in his mind. First: you must know where your time should be spent! Time is very much\\n\\nLimited, treat your time well, never play mahjong or waste time drinking. Every company has many things to deal with and think about. Where you spend your time, where is your performance.\\n\\nSecond: Always think about what contribution you can make to the market. We do not work for the sake of work, but for the market. We do not dive into technology and methods as soon as we arrive at the company. We should first ask ourselves a question, what do customers want me to do? Then I will do something.\\n\\nThird: Only use your own strengths to do things, use the strengths of team members to do things. Do not\\n\\nEntrepreneur Business School Serving Entrepreneurs 127\\n\\nBut build your work on your own shortcomings and never do things you can't do. Don't do what you don't want to do. Ask employees to do things that can't be bypassed.\\n\\nFourth: Focus on a few important things. According to the Rule of 28, the most profitable business of a company must be the 20% of its core business, which contributes 80% of its profits. Therefore, we have to focus on that small part of our core business. We prioritize our daily work according to the priority and adhere to this order. The most important things are first, the important things are done first, and the unimportant things are let go. Only in this way can we increase the business volume of the company.\\n\\nFifth: What the boss has to do is to make strategic decisions, and tactical decisions are made by others in the team. It is important to realize that good strategies are always discussed in different opinions. It is not necessary to make decisions quickly. Important decisions can even be made after going home to sleep. Or have more meetings and discussions, and most of the quick decisions will make you regret it.\",\"timestamp\":1634796613,\"title\":\"5 habits that the boss must cultivate in his mind\"},\"digest\":\"cE99BvjnsrzPfRaJkd8hT8EiTcmlQYoJxuHd_T4B8go\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0500e3b6f7b1214a11851b9B348020C08018403b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"SBvWKfIAxm5lNQwX0ZwhFR1ogMG8xF06Kd27i1I1T-P6oRhsvPr_tPycRTwi5Vv-ThKA0_P1S6pE2hThpDzVJw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1c6f856baad7dbcdc04a289cfb8c27fd2d4c254469eae7a6d5e283ce19250e091ab85676074d27b49e23c7d4b78b5f81e8536a0da448b30920c0f4dc5a6602e41c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"cE99BvjnsrzPfRaJkd8hT8EiTcmlQYoJxuHd_T4B8go\"}"